th%20Israel%20over%20the%20rocket%20strikes%20launched%20by%20Hamas%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20on%20October%207%20that%20India's%20thoughts%20and%20prayers%20are%20with%20the%20innocent%20victims%20and%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeeply%20shocked%20by%20the%20news%20of%20terrorist%20attacks%20in%20Israel.%20Our%20thoughts%20and%20prayers%20are%20with%20the%20innocent%20victims%20and%20their%20families.%20We%20stand%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Israel%20at%20this%20difficult%20hour%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20posted%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20heated%20political%20exchange%20emerged%20on%20Wednesday%20surrounding%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%2C%20with%20leaders%20from%20various%20parties%20expressing%20contrasting%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20also%20expressed%20his%20dismay%20at%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20remarks%2C%20emphasising%20the%20need%20to%20condemn%20terrorism%20worldwide.%20Mr%20Goyal%20pointed%20out%20that%20Pawar%20had%20held%20prominent%20positions%20in%20the%20government%20during%20critical%20security%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20disturbing%20when%20a%20senior%20leader%20like%20Sharad%20Pawar%20makes%20preposterous%20statements%20on%20India's%20stand%20on%20a%20terror%20attack%20in%20Israel.%20The%20menace%20of%20terrorism%20has%20to%20be%20condemned%20in%20all%20forms%2C%20in%20any%20part%20of%20the%20world.%20It%20is%20a%20pity%20that%20a%20person%20who%20has%20been%20India's%20Defence%20Minister%20as%20well%20as%20a%20Chief%20Minister%20many%20times%20has%20such%20a%20casual%20view%20of%20issues%20relating%20to%20terror%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPawar%20ji%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20same%20Government%20that%20shed%20tears%20on%20the%20Batla%20House%20encounter%20and%20slept%20while%20there%20were%20terror%20attacks%20on%20Indian%20soil.%20This%20rotten%20m