%3EUK%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20will%20visit%20Israel%20today%20to%20meet%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20and%20President%20Isaac%20Herzog%20before%20travelling%20to%20other%20capitals%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20his%20office%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697679540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fdqq4pmlg_rafah-border-crossing-afp-_625x300_19_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-rafah-border-crossing-gaza-palestine-egypt-agrees-to-open-gaza-aid-corridor-after-talks-with-biden-10-facts-4494537%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Egypt%20has%20announced%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bsustainable%26quot%3B%20humanitarian%20aid%20corridor%20into%20Gaza.%20The%20announcement%20comes%20as%20hundreds%20of%20trucks%2C%20carrying%20essential%20supplies%2C%20are%20waiting%20to%20enter%20the%20besieged%20Palestinian%20enclave%20being%20bombarded%20by%20Israel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-rafah-border-crossing-gaza-palestine-egypt-agrees-to-open-gaza-aid-corridor-after-talks-with-biden-10-facts-4494537%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-rafah-border-crossing-gaza-palestine-egypt-agrees-to-open-gaza-aid-corridor-after-talks-with-biden-10-facts-4494537%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-rafah-border-crossing-gaza-palestine-egypt-agrees-to-open-gaza-aid-corridor-after-talks-with-biden-10-facts-4494537%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20considers%20removing%20X%20platform%20from%20Europe%20over%20EU%20law%3A%20Insider%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697679537000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104539798%2Cimgsi