tions%20about%20company%20communications%2C%20Katz%20maintained%20that%20most%20of%20the%20evidence%20shown%20to%20her%20had%20been%20drafted%20and%20published%20before%20her%20time%20at%20the%20company%20from%20April%20to%20November%20of%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%20called%20essentially%20as%20a%20mannequin%20to%20read%20to%20the%20jury%20documents%20in%20evidence%20and%20the%20transcripts%20of%20videotapes%20in%20evidence%2C%20and%20that%20was%20a%20waste%20of%20her%20time%2C%20it%20was%20a%20waste%20of%20the%20jury's%20time%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20waste%20of%20everybody%20else's%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaplan%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20expect%20different%20behavior%20from%20counsel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20the%20day%2C%20the%20prosecution%20called%20Cory%20Gaddis%2C%20a%20records%20custodian%20at%20Google%20who%20flew%20to%20New%20York%20from%20Texas.%20He%20was%20also%20unable%20to%20answer%20most%20of%20the%20questions%20he%20was%20asked%20about%20specific%20document%20metadata.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20we%20are%20treated%20to%20this%20Mr.%20Gaddis%20being%20hauled%20up%20here%20from%20Texas%20to%20authenticate%20metadata%20on%2C%20I%20believe%20it%20was%20five%20documents%2C%20maybe%20it's%20seven%20or%20eight%2C%20as%20to%20which%20there%20was%20no%20dispute%20at%20all%20to%20get%20them%20into%20evidence%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaplan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20going%20to%20do%20this%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20noting%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bfault%20on%20both%20sides.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaplan's%20complaints%20aside%2C%20Wednesday%20was%20an%20otherwise%20efficient%20trial%20day%2C%20with%20four%20witnesses%20taking%20the%20stand%20in%20total.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeter%20Easton%2C%20an%20accounting%20professor%20and%20academic%20director%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Notre%20Dame%2C%20testified%20extensively%20about%20analyses%20he%20did%20on%20FTX's%20and%20Alameda's%20finances.%3C%