3Cp%3EAn%20expert%20on%20floor%20plans%20for%20these%20types%20of%20structures%2C%20he%20surmised%20there%20might%20be%20storage%20rooms%20beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20would%20take%20another%20nearly%20200%20years%20to%20finally%20confirm%20his%20suspicions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20hidden%20storage%20rooms%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20area%20was%20so%20damaged%20it%20was%20impossible%20to%20enter%2C%20so%20Perring%20had%20no%20way%20of%20knowing%20if%20he%20was%20right.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDecades%20later%2C%20German%20Egyptologist%20Ludwig%20Borchardt%20ignored%20Perring's%20claims%20when%20he%20was%20excavating%20the%20site%20in%20the%20early%201900s.%20If%20he'd%20looked%20closer%2C%20history%20might%20have%20been%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20a%20joint%20Egyptian-German%20team%20working%20to%20restore%20the%20pyramid%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uni-wuerzburg.de%2Fen%2Fnews-and-events%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2Fnews%2Fneue-raeume-in-der-pyramide-von-sahura-entdeckt%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20shown%3C%2Fa%3E%20Perring%20was%20correct.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fancient-civilizations-that-were-hiding-in-plain-sight-2023-1%5C%22%3EUsing%20lidar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20method%20that%20applies%20laser%20pulses%20to%20penetrate%20obstacles%20like%20tree%20canopies%20or%20walls%20to%20see%20what%20lies%20beyond%2C%20the%20researchers%20mapped%20the%20exterior%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkhufu-pyramid-big-room-chamber-void-muons-physics-2017-11%5C%22%3Einterior%20passages%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20chambers.%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETemperature%20changes%2C%20high%20humidity%2C%20and%20windy%20conditions%20have%20helped%20cause%20certain%20parts%20of%20the%20pyramid%20to%20collapse%20over%20the%20centuries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClearing%20some%20of%20the%20rubble%20and%20creating%203D%20maps%20have%20allowed%20the%20researchers%20to%20get%20a%20better%20sense%20of%20the%20structure%2C%20including%20eight%20previously%20hidden%20rooms%20off%20the%20passage%20Perring%20found.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20newly%20discovered%20chambers%20are%20likely%20storage%20rooms%2C%20meant%20to%20hold%20burial%20objects%20belonging%20to%20royal%20rulers%2C%20according%20to%20Egyptologist%20Mohamed%20Ismail%20Khaled%20from%20Julius-Maximilians-Universit%C3%A4t%20of%20W%C3%BCrzburg%2C%20who%20led%20the%20restoration%20team.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESahure's%20Pyramid%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20structure%20is%20located%20in%20the%20Abusir%20pyramid%20complex%2C%20just%20south%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreat-pyramid-giza-egypt-2019-2%5C%22%3Eof%20Giza%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blocks%20and%20pillars%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Pyramid%20of%20Sahure%20in%20Egypt%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65302f9496f7540cd05fb862%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20mortuary%20temple%20and%20Pyramid%20of%20Sahure%20at%20the%20Necropolis%20of%20Abusir.%3Cp%3EDeAgostini%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESahure%20was%20a%20pharaoh%20who%20ruled%20during%20the%20Fifth%20Dynasty%2C%20around%202%2C400%20BCE.%20One%20document%20suggests%20Sahure%20wasn't%20of%20royal%20lineage%2C%20but%20was%20said%20to%20be%20the%20son%20of%20Ra%2C%20the%20sun%20deity.%20As%20with%20other%20pharaohs%2C%20his%20pyramid%20stood%20as%20a%20monument%20to%20his%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pyramid%20of%20Sahura%20has%20been%20excavated%20numerous%20times%20in%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBorchardt%20left%20a%20decent%20portion%20of%20the%20pyramid%20unexplored.%20In%201994%2C%20a%20new%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farce.org%2Fchanging-old-paradigms-new-evidence-pyramid-complex-sahura-abusir%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexcavation%20began%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20uncovering%20huge%20limestone%20blocks%20covered%20with%20multi-colored%20images.%20One%20shows%20Sahure%20sailing%20on%20a%20boat%2C%20with%20a%20fleet%20of%20boats%20behind%2C%20with%20some%20bows%20decorated%20with%20lion%20or%20eagle%20heads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20pyramid%20is%20falling%20apart%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20reason%20the%20pyramid%20is%20in%20such%20disrepair%20is%20due%20to%20the%20original%20construction%20techniques.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20core%20contains%20bits%20of%20limestone%2C%20pieces%20of%20pottery%2C%20sand%2C%20and%20other%20rubble.%20While%20it%20cut%20construction%20time%20and%20cost%2C%20the%20technique%20may%20have%20left%20the%20pyramid%20more%20prone%20to%20collapse%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Farticle%2F10.1186%2Fs40494-022-00699-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2022%20study%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20conservation%20project%20started%20in%202019.%20The%20team%20is%20working%20to%20stabilize%20the%20structure%2C%20replacing%20crumbling%20supports%20with%20retaining%20walls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hope%20is%20to%20clean%20and%20secure%20the%20chambers%20and%20potentially%20open%20the%20pyramid%20to%20the%20public%20in%20the%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpyramid-hidden-rooms-lidar-egypt-sahure-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697669048000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653030a6211def8ed838782f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpyramid-hidden-rooms-lidar-egypt-sahure-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Using%20lidar%2C%20researchers%20found%20hidden%20storage