ral%20finance%20policy%20has%20not%20moved%20as%20fast%20as%20local%20governments%20have.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20adjustment%20in%20Federal%20Housing%20Administration%20policy%20is%20a%20big%20step%20towards%20changing%20that.%20As%20of%20October%2016%2C%20federally%20insured%20mortgage%20providers%20like%20Fannie%20Mae%20and%20Freddie%20Mac%20will%20allow%20homeowners%20to%20list%20projected%20rental%20income%20of%20an%20ADU%20when%20applying%20for%20a%20mortgage%20to%20build%20one%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fstatements-releases%2F2023%2F10%2F16%2Fwhite-house-announces-new-actions-on-homeownership%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhite%20House%20said%20Monday%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Previously%2C%20homeowners%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20list%20this%20as%20income.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20flexibilities%20will%20help%20more%20first-time%20homebuyers%2C%20seniors%2C%20and%20inter-generational%20families%20leverage%20ADUs%20to%20build%20generational%20wealth%20through%20homeownership%20while%20creating%20new%20affordable%20housing%20in%20their%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20White%20House%20officials%20said%20in%20the%20announcement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20this%20means%20and%20who%20it%20affects%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFannie%20and%20Freddie%20set%20the%20standard%20for%20banks%20everywhere%2C%20so%20this%20will%20generally%20make%20ADU%20financing%20more%20accessible%2C%20Ryan%20O'Connell%2C%20founder%20of%20California-based%20ADU%20advocacy%20company%20How%20To%20ADU%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBroadly%2C%20everyone%20who%20offers%20FHA%20203(k)%20products%20%E2%80%94%20a%20type%20of%20federally%20supported%20mortgage%20%E2%80%94%20will%20%26quot%3Bstart%20counting%20rental%20income%20when%20allowed%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Connell%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22one%20of%20the%20ADU%20grant%20recipents%2C%20Jakota%20Rivas%2C%20in%20front%20of%20he