ion%20in%20student-debt%20cancellation%20is%20on%20the%20way%20for%20borrowers%20who%20went%20to%20a%20for-profit%20school%20that%20'falsely'%20touted%20job%20placement%20rates%2C%20the%20FTC%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225734%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22President%20Joe%20Biden%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F645b9c6465a21600192fe88e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223823%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EU.S.%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%3Cp%3EAnna%20Moneymaker%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20FTC%20reached%20a%20settlement%20with%20for-profit%20Sollers%20College%20to%20resolve%20claims%20of%20illegal%20behavior.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESollers%20will%20cancel%20%243.4%20million%20in%20student%20debt%20for%20those%20who%20entered%20income-share%20agreements.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20FTC%20said%20the%20school%20lied%20about%20job%20placement%20rates%20and%20employer%20partnerships.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERelief%20is%20on%20the%20way%20for%20some%20student-loan%20borrowers%20who%20went%20to%20a%20school%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20administration%20accused%20of%20illegal%20behavior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ftc.gov%2Fnews-events%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2F2023%2F10%2Fsollers-college-cancel-34-million-student-debt-resolve-charges-it-used-deceptive-ads-lure%3Futm_source%3Dgovdelivery%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Sollers%20College%20%E2%80%94%20a%20for-profit%20school%20based%20in%20New%20Jersey%20%E2%80%94%20has%20to%20cancel%20%243.4%20million%20in%20student%20debt%20to%20resolve%20accusations%20the%20FTC%20and%20the%20state%20of%20New%20Jersey%20brought%20against%20the%20school%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Bfalsely%26quot%3B%20touting%20job%20placement%20rates%2C%20per%20the%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20according%20to%20the%20FTC's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ftc.gov%2Fsystem%2Ffiles%2Fftc_gov%2Fpdf%2F01-Complaint.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomplaint%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sollers%20misrepresented%20its%20relationship%20with%20prominent%20companies%20that%20it%20said%20would%20hire%20students%20after%20they%20graduated.%20The%20agency%20also%20accused%20Sollers%20of%20pushing%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B%20income-share%20agreements%2C%20in%20which%20students%20agreed%20to%20pay%20Sollers%20a%20fixed%20percentage%20of%20their%20future%20income%20on%20a%20monthly%20basis%20to%20repay%20tuition%20costs.%20The%20FTC%20said%20the%20school%20entered%20392%20%26quot%3Billegal%20agreements%26quot%3B%20between%20August%202018%20and%202021%20for%20failing%20to%20include%20a%20notice%20that%20protects%20consumers%20when%20they%20enter%20those%20types%20of%20agreements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20only%20did%20Sollers%20College%20use%20deceptive%20advertisements%20to%20attract%20students%2C%20it%20trapped%20them%20in%20multi-year%20income%20share%20agreements%20that%20broke%20the%20law%20by%20leaving%20out%20important%20borrower%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20Samuel%20Levine%2C%20Director%20of%20the%20FTC's%20Bureau%20of%20Consumer%20Protection%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BToday's%20order%20cancels%20all%20income-share%20agreements%20issued%20by%20the%20school.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20settlement%2C%20Sollers%20is%20required%20to%20notify%20all%20students%20who%20will%20receive%20relief%20within%20the%20next%2015%20days%20either%20by%20email%20or%20written%20notice%2C%20and%20the%20school%20is%20prohibited%20from%20denying%20access%20to%20transcripts%20or%20diplomas%20due%20to%20any%20debt%20the%20student%20might%20hold.%20Sollers%20will%20also%20ask%20credit%20bureaus%20Experian%2C%20Equifax%2C%20and%20TransUnion%20to%20delete%20the%20debt%20from%20borrowers'%20credit%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20notice%20will%20say%3A%20%26quot%3BWe're%20writing%20because%20you%20have%20an%20income%20share%20agreement%20with%20Sollers%20College.%20The%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%20(FTC)%2C%20the%20nation's%20consumer%20protection%20agency%2C%20sued%20us%20because%20they%20said%20we%20used%20deceptive%20ads%20and%20didn't%20tell%20you%20about%20some%20of%20your%20rights%20in%20our%20income%20share%20agreements.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESollers%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20accusations%20within%20FTC's%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20accusations%20have%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20some%20businesses%20that%20Sollers%20said%20it%20had%20partnerships%20with.%20For%20example%2C%20Weill%20Cornell%20Medicine%20%E2%80%94%20a%20company%20Sollers%20touted%20for%20employment%20opportunities%20%E2%80%94%20sent%20the%20school%20a%20cease-and-desist%20letter%20in%202022%20demanding%20Sollers%20remove%20the%20company's%20logo%20because%20it%20never%20agreed%20to%20a%20partnership.%20Aerotek%2C%20another%20company%2C%20demanded%20Sollers%20do%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20according%20to%20the%20FTC's%20complaint%2C%20about%2090%25%20of%20students%20who%20entered%20income-share%20agreements%20with%20Sollers%20are%20%26quot%3Beither%20actively%20in%20repayment%20or%20defaulted%20on%20their%20agreements%20and%20now%20owe%20Sollers%20a%20fixed%20amount%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20Sollers%20had%20sent%20those%20students%20to%20debt%20collection%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20a%20federal%20agency%20has%20raised%20red%20flags%20over%20income-share%20agreements.%20The%20Consumer%20Financial%20Protection%20Bureau%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcfpb-states-sue-prehired-predatory-student-debt-tech-bootcamp-isa-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecently%20sued%20career%20bootcamp%20Prehired%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20misrepresenting%20the%20nature%20of%20its%20income-share%20agreements%20with%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrehired%20failed%20to%20advise%20consumers%20about%20the%20cost%20of%20these%20loans%2C%20and%20deceptively%20represented%20that%20the%20ISAs%20are%20not%20loans%20and%20did%20not%20create%20debt%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CFPB's%20complaint%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-who-qualifies-sollers-college-debt-relief-ftc-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697658539000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653027afbe9edfa8eda3f843%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-who-qualifies-sollers-college-debt-relief-ftc-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20FTC%20said%20student-loan%20borrowers%20who%20went%20to%20Sollers%20College%20were%20lured%20into%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B%20income-share%20agreements%20that%20surged%20their%20debt.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-who-qualifies-sollers-college-debt-relief-ftc-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prabhas'%20aunt%20talks%20about%20his%20wedding%20plans%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697658371000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104536114%2Cimgsize-38842.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fprabhas-aunt-shyamala-devi-spills-the-beans-on-his-wedding-plans-we-will-invite-all-media-for-the-marriage-and-celebrate-it%2Farticleshow%2F104536107.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto