n%202021%20that%20she%20was%20finally%20given%20back%20all%20her%20legal%20rights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20in%20her%20upcoming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Frepeatedly-told-me-britney-spears-reveals-being-body-shamed-by-father-during-conservatorship-4491987%5C%22%3Ememoir%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20'The%20Woman%20in%20Me'%2C%20Ms%20Spears%20has%20reflected%20on%20the%20highs%20and%20lows%20throughout%20her%20tumultuous%20career.%20Specifically%2C%20in%20an%20excerpt%20obtained%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Fbritney-spears-reveals-why-shaved-off-hair-in-2007-exclusive-8362494%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPeople%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20pop%20icon%20explained%20why%20she%20cut%20off%20all%20her%20hair%20ahead%20of%20her%20conservatorship.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20been%20eyeballed%20so%20much%20growing%20up.%20I'd%20been%20looked%20up%20and%20down%2C%20had%20people%20telling%20me%20what%20they%20thought%20of%20my%20body%2C%20since%20I%20was%20a%20teenager%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20singer%20wrote%20in%20an%20excerpt.%20%26quot%3BShaving%20my%20head%20and%20acting%20out%20were%20my%20ways%20of%20pushing%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Ms%20Spears%20was%20also%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20her%20divorce%20from%20ex-husband%20Kevin%20Federline%20while%20simultaneously%20fighting%20for%20custody%20over%20their%20two%20sons%2C%20Jayden%20and%20Sean.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fai-reads-words-on-ancient-scroll-burned-in-mount-vesuvius-eruption-4492422%5C%22%3EAI%20Reads%20Words%20On%20Ancient%20Scroll%20Burned%20In%20Mount%20Vesuvius%20Eruption%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2041-year-old%20in%20her%20memoir%20said%20once%20her%20father%20took%20control%20of%20her%20personal%2C%20medical%20and%20financial%20affairs%20in%202008%2C%20she%20no%20longer%20had%20a%20say%20in%20her%20day-to-day%20life.%20She%20said%20she%20was%20forbidden%20from%20keeping%20the%20new%20look.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20made%20to%20understand%20that%20those%20days%20were%20now%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20to%20grow%20my%20hair%20out%20and%20get%20back%20into%20shape.%20I%20had%20to%20go%20to%20bed%20early%20and%20take%20whatever%20medication%20they%20told%20me%20to%20take.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EElsewhere%20in%20an%20excerpt%20from%20her%20memoir%2C%20Ms%20Spears%20opened%20up%20about%20her%20conservatorship%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bstripped%20me%20of%20my%20womanhood%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20conservatorship%20stripped%20me%20of%20my%20womanhood%2C%20made%20me%20into%20a%20child.%20I%20became%20more%20of%20an%20entity%20than%20a%20person%20onstage.%20I%20had%20always%20felt%20music%20in%20my%20bones%20and%20my%20blood%3B%20they%20stole%20that%20from%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20she%20also%20said%20that%20she%20%26quot%3Bdidn't%20deserve%26quot%3B%20what%20her%20family%20did%20to%20her.%20%26quot%3BThe%20woman%20in%20me%20was%20pushed%20down%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20They%20wanted%20me%20to%20be%20wild%20onstage%20...%20and%20to%20be%20a%20robot%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20memoir%2C%20'The%20Woman%20in%20Me'%20is%20set%20to%20be%20released%20on%20October%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697652840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fblcvl8ag_-britney-spears_625x300_12_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbritney-spears-explains-why-she-shaved-off-her-hair-in-2007-4494285%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%2016%20years%2C%20American%20singer%20Britney%20Spears%20has%20finally%20revealed%20the%20reason%20behind%20her%20infamous%202007%20head-shaving%20stunt.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22