urt-4494279%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fenforcement-directorate-special-powers-challenged-again-in-top-court-4494279%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fenforcement-directorate-special-powers-challenged-again-in-top-court-4494279%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHas%20Got%20Down%20To%20A%20Rot%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Notice%20To%20Company%20Tribunal%20Members%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EObserving%20that%20the%20National%20Company%20Law%20Appellate%20Tribunal%20has%20got%20down%20to%20a%20rot%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20issued%20notices%20to%20tribunal's%20judicial%20member%20Rakesh%20Kumar%20and%20technical%20member%20Alok%20Srivastava%20asking%20why%20contempt%20proceedings%20be%20not%20initiated%20against%20them%20for%20defying%20apex%20court%20orders%20in%20the%20Finolex%20Cables%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20took%20strong%20exception%20to%20the%20passing%20of%20a%20judgement%20by%20the%20NCLAT%20bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20NCLAT%20bench%20had%20delivered%20a%20judgement%20on%20October%2013%20ignoring%20a%20status%20quo%20order%20passed%20by%20the%20apex%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20set%20aside%20the%20NCLAT%20bench's%20October%2013%20judgement%20relating%20to%20the%20annual%20general%20meeting%20(AGM)%20of%20Finolex%20Cables%20without%20going%20into%20its%20merit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20also%20comprising%20Justices%20JB%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%20said%20the%20case%20would%20be%20heard%20by%20NCLAT%20chief%20Justice%20Ashok%20Bhushan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNCLT%20and%20NCLAT%20have%20got%20down%20to%20a%20rot%20now.%20This%20case%20is%20an%20illustration%20of%20that%20rot.%20We%20are%20prima%20facie%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20members%20of%20the%20NCLAT%20have%20failed%20to%20disclose%20correct%20facts%20and%20incorrectly%20created%20a%20record%20in%20the%20order%20dated%2016%20October%20that%20this%20court's%20order%20was%20drawn%20to%20their%20notice%20on%205.35%20pm%20on%2013%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20of%20the%20view%20that%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20pass%20orders%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20dignity%20of%20this%20court%20is%20restored.%20Parties%20cannot%20be%20allowed%20by%20recourse%20to%20devious%20means%20to%20obviate%20this%20court's%20orders%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20also%20cautioned%20corporates%20attempting%20to%20subvert%20court%20orders%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20our%20orders%20are%20being%20subverted%20then%20Corporate%20India%20should%20know%20that%20there%20is%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20who%20is%20watching.%20That%20is%20all%20we%20wish%20to%20say%20now.%26quot%3B%20The%20order%20is%20related%20to%20the%20annual%20general%20meeting%20(AGM)%20of%20Finolex%20Cables%20and%20Prakash%20Chhabria%20and%20Deepak%20Chhabria's%20legal%20tussle%20over%20the%20management%20control%20of%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20rare%20for%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20issue%20contempt%20notices%20against%20NCLAT%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20last%20Friday%20had%20directed%20the%20NCLAT%20chairperson%20to%20conduct%20an%20enquiry%20and%20submit%20a%20report%20by%20Monday%20over%20an%20allegation%20that%20one%20of%20its%20benches%20proceeded%20and%20delivered%20an%20order%20without%20following%20the%20top%20court's%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20three-member%20apex%20court%20bench%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20had%20on%20that%20day%20directed%20the%20NCLAT%20to%20proceed%20to%20its%20judgment%20and%20declare%20the%20results%20of%20the%20meeting%20only%20after%20getting%20the%20scrutiniser's%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20order%20was%20uploaded%20at%201.55%20pm%20and%20the%20counsel%20also%20informed%20the%20development%20to%20the%20NCLAT%20bench%2C%20which%20was%20scheduled%20to%20deliver%20the%20judgment%20at%202%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20two-member%20bench%20of%20the%20NCLAT%20comprising%20Justice%20Kumar%2C%20Member%20Judicial%2C%20and%20Srivastava%2C%20Member%20Technical%2C%20went%20ahead%20and%20pronounced%20the%20order%2C%20while%20the%20scrutiniser's%20report%20was%20uploaded%20at%202%3A40%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20was%20apprised%20about%20the%20development%20through%20an%20urgent%20mentioning%20by%20lawyers%20and%20the%20bench%20led%20by%20the%20chief%20justice%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20what%20is%20stated%20is%20correct%2C%20this%20will%20clearly%20constitute%20the%20defiance%20of%20the%20order%20of%20this%20court%20by%20the%20NCLAT.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20it%20also%20said%20that%20at%20this%20stage%20it%20is%20not%20commenting%20on%20the%20merits%20of%20the%20submissions%20which%20have%20been%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20direct%20that%20an%20enquiry%20shall%20be%20conducted%20on%20the%20above%20allegations%20by%20the%20Chairperson%20of%20the%20NCLAT.%20A%20report%20shall%20be%20submitted%20before%20this%20court%20by%205%20pm%20on%2016%20October%202023%20after%20specifically%20verifying%20the%20facts%20from%20the%20judges%20who%20constituted%20the%20bench%20of%20the%20NCLAT%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20apex%20court%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20expressed%20dissatisfaction%20with%20the%20NCLAT%20members'%20explanation%20that%20as%20per%20the%20procedure%20in%20NCLAT%2C%20oral%20mentionings%20are%20allowed%20only%20after%20the%20pronouncement%20of%20the%20judgment%20and%20therefore%20the%20lawyers%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20mention%20the%20top%20court's%20order%20before%20the%20pronouncement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20said%20the%20NCLAT%20chairperson%20shall%20specifically%20verify%20%26quot%3Bthat%20the%20order%20of%20this%20court%20dated%2013%20October%202023%20passed%20in%20the%20morning%20session%20was%20drawn%20to%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20two%20judges%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20that%20is%20so%2C%20the%20circumstances%20in%20which%20the%20judges%20proceeded%20to%20pronounce%20the%20judgment%20despite%20the%20clear%20mandate%20of%20the%20order%20of%20this%20court%20which%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20morning%20session%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court's%20order%20came%20over%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20Prakash%20Chhabria-led%20Orbit%20Electricals%20which%20is%20a%20promoter%20entity%20in%20Finolex%20Cables.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20sought%20disclosure%20of%20the%20outcome%20of%20voting%20in%20the%20AGM%20of%20the%20company%20on%20the%20agenda%20item%20pertaining%20to%20the%20reappointment%20of%20Deepak%20Chhabria%20as%20executive%20chairman.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20challenged%20the%20non-disclosure%20of%20the%20outcome%20of%20voting%20by%20shareholders%20pertaining%20to%20the%20resolution%20related%20to%20the%20reappointment%20of%20Deepak%20Chhabria%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BWhole-Time%20Director%26quot%3B%20designated%20as%20an%20%26quot%3BExecutive%20Chairman%26quot%3B%20in%20its%20AGM%20held%20on%20September%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20this%20matter%2C%20the%20NCLAT%20had%20on%20September%2021%20passed%20an%20order%20directing%20the%20status%20quo%20on%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20AGM%2C%20till%20they%20adjudicate%20on%20the%20dispute%20between%20cousins%20Prakash%20Chhabria%20and%20Deepak%20Chhabria.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20this%2C%20an%20appeal%20was%20referred%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20had%20on%20September%2026%20vacated%20this%20status%20quo%20order%20and%20said%20all%20action%20which%20may%20be%20taken%20would%20abide%20by%20the%20final%20result%20of%20the%20proceedings%20before%20NCLAT.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20NCLAT%20shall%20proceed%20to%20declare%20its%20judgment%20in%20the%20pending%20appeal%20after%20it%20is%20duly%20apprised%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20result%20of%20the%20annual%20general%20meeting%20has%20been%20declared%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20apex%20court%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697652540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fp4eevs58_supreme-court_625x300_24_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhas-got-down-to-a-rot-sc-issues-contempt-notices-to-nclat-members-in-finolex-cables-case-4493420%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Observing%20that%20the%20National%20Company%20Law%20Appellate%20Tribunal%20has%20got%20down%20to%20a%20rot%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20issued%20notices%20to%20tribunal's%20judicial%20member%20Rakesh%20Kumar%20and%20technical%20member%20Alok%20Srivastava.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhas-got-down-to-a-rot-sc-issues-contempt-notices-to-nclat-members-in-finolex-cables-case-4493420%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhas-got-down-to-a-rot-sc-issues-contempt-notices-to-nclat-members-in-finolex-cables-case-4493420%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhas-got-down-to-a-rot-sc-issues-contempt-notices-to-nclat-members-in-finolex-cables-case-4493420%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bhumi%20on%20her%20bold%20scenes%20in%20Thank%20You%20for%20Coming%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697652350000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104535300%2Cimgsize-71162.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbhumi-pednekar-opens-up-about-her-bold-scenes-in-thank-you-for-coming-i-was-fully-cl