ace.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FuU4pYWQA4x%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FuU4pYWQA4x%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Cam%20Botanic%20Garden%20(%40CUBotanicGarden)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCUBotanicGarden%2Fstatus%2F1494968340011524099%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2019%2C%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20report%2C%20the%20garden%20artist-in-residence%20Nabil%20Ali%20extracted%20ink%20from%20its%20bark%20and%20used%20the%20product%20to%20make%20an%20artwork%20of%2068%20apples.%20To%20make%20the%20ink%2C%20he%20peeled%20away%20some%20of%20the%20bark%20and%20soaked%20it%20for%20a%20day-and-a-half%20in%20his%20workshop%20before%20grinding%20it%2C%20boiling%20it%20to%20release%20the%20tannin%2C%20and%20adding%20the%20chemical%20compound%20alum.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E''To%20our%20knowledge%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20anyone%20has%20discovered%20the%20colours%20hidden%20within%20a%20descendent%20of%20Newton's%20inspiring%20tree.%20I%20thought%20I'd%20end%20up%20with%20black%20pigment%20but%20it's%20a%20dark%20golden%20yellow.%20I'm%20calling%20it%20Newton's%20Gold%2C''%20Mr%20Ali%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20exhibit%20featuring%20the%20replicas%20of%20the%2068%20apples%20will%20premiere%20on%20Apple%20Day%20on%20October%2022%20at%20the%20university's%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Samuel%20Brockington%2C%20curator%20of%20Cambridge%20University's%20Botanic%20Garden%2C%20said%20the%20genome%20of%20the%20Cambridge%20tree%20was%20sequenced%20by%20the%20Darwin%20Tree%20of%20Life%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20this%20analysis%2C%20our%20tree%20seems%20identical%20to%20other%20descendants%2C%20and%20so%20we%20can%20say%20with%20confidence%20that%20ours%20is%20a%20direct%20clone%20of%20the%20original%20tree%20in%20Grantham%2C%20which%20also%20fell%20in%20a%20gale%20in%20the%2019th%20century%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20Mr.%20Ali's%20creation%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20so%20pleased%20that%20Nabil%20has%20managed%20to%20sample%20its%20colour.%20His%20work%20is%20an%20inspiring%20way%20of%20engaging%20people%20in%20the%20natural%20world%20through%20art%20and%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20original%20tree%2C%20grown%20in%20the%20garden%20of%20Newton's%20childhood%20home%20of%20Woolsthorpe%20Manor%20near%20Grantham%20in%20Lincolnshire%2C%20was%20said%20to%20have%20fallen%20in%20a%20gale%20in%20the%20early%20half%20of%20the%2019th%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697640720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fmc40q99_newtons-apple-tree_625x300_18_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcambridge-university-artist-creates-unique-ink-from-clone-of-isaac-newtons-apple-tree-4493558%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20clone%20was%20planted%20at%20Cambridge%20Universitys%20Botanic%20Garden%20in%201954%20and%20fell%20in%20high%20winds%20in%20February%202022%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcambridge-university-artist-creates-unique-ink-from-clone-of-isaac-newtons-apple-tree-4493558%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcambridge-university-artist-creates-unique-ink-from-clone-of-isaac-newtons-apple-tree-4493558%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcambridge-university-artist-creates-unique-ink-from-clone-of-isaac-newtons-apple-tree-4493558%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fire%20destroys%20Iowa%20wind%20turbine%20after%20emergency%20workers%20fail%20to%20reach%20top%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697640688000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F9318%2Fproduction%2F_131465673_p0gm8l1s.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.c