ntages%20of%20gardening%20and%20encourages%20everyone%20to%20connect%20with%20nature.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332547%2Fsooraj-purushothaman-organic-farmer-kerala-gardening-growing-vegetables%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20%E2%80%98Double%20Engine%E2%80%99%20is%20Pass%C3%A9%2C%20Hereafter%20Modi-Shah%20Will%20Pick%20or%20Junk%20BJP%20CMs%20at%20Will%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F05%2F27230635%2FScreenshot-2022-05-27-at-11.06.15-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20selection%20of%20BJP%20candidates%20for%20the%20ensuing%20assembly%20elections%20signals%20two%20significant%20trends%20%E2%80%93%20both%20leading%20to%20further%20centralisation%20of%20power%20in%20the%20top%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20trend%20is%20the%20diminishing%20role%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20central%20election%20committee%20where%2C%20in%20an%20earlier%20era%2C%C2%A0%20senior%20leaders%20discussed%20the%20pros%20and%20cons%20of%20each%20candidate.%20Now%20Amit%20Shah%20visits%20each%20state%2C%20discusses%20the%20situation%20and%20draws%20up%20a%20list%20which%20the%20election%20committee%2C%20if%20at%20all%20it%20meets%2C%20approves.%20It%20is%20not%20at%20all%20like%20the%20meetings%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20national%20executive%2C%20once%20known%20for%20lively%20debates%20by%20Jaswant%20Singh%2C%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20second%20signal%20is%20more%20sweeping%20and%20aimed%20at%20wiping%20out%20the%20established%20hierarchies%20in%20states.%20In%20one%20stroke%2C%20Shah%20has%20negated%20powerful%20state%20leaders%20like%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20Scindia%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20four-time%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Hereafter%2C%20nominees%20handpicked%20by%20Modi-Shah%20will%20head%20all%20state%20governments%20%E2%80%93%20in%20true%20high%20command%20style.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20wipe%20out%20the%20remaining%20pockets%20of%20small%20fiefdoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20appointment%20culture%20is%20an%20old%20Congress%20tradition.%20But%20Congress%20first%20sent%20central%20observers%20to%20the%20states%2C%20tried%20for%20a%20consensus%20candidate%20or%20in%20the%20alternative%20took%20the%20views%20of%20individual%20MLAs.%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20done%20away%20with%20even%20such%20niceties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERegional%20leaders%20of%20all%20parties%20cultivate%20cadre%20who%20are%20personally%20loyal%20to%20them%3B%20in%20turn%2C%20these%20leaders%20provide%20them%20with%20tickets%20and%20funds.%20Such%20fiefdoms%20strengthened%20the%20party.%20Now%20Modi%20wants%20to%20demolish%20these%20vestiges%20of%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20was%20how%20Vijay%20Rupani%20was%20removed%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Felections%2Fassembly-elections%2Fgujarat%2Fnews%2Fbhupendra-patel-takes-oath-as-gujarat-cm-for-second-time%2Farticleshow%2F96168805.cms%5C%22%3Erelatively%20unknown%20Bhupendra%20Patel%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0imposed%20on%20Gujarat%20in%202021.%20Many%20veterans%20protested%20and%20threatened%20to%20keep%20off%20the%20swearing%20ceremony%20but%20meekly%20surrendered%20later.%20Among%20them%20were%20Nitin%20Patel%2C%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%2C%20Gordhan%20Zafadia%20and%20Praful%20Patel.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fconsolidate-patidar-votes-retain-others-support%2Farticleshow%2F86148532.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3EGujarat%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20now%20being%20replicated%20in%20all%20BJP%20strongholds.%20Hereafter%2C%20as%20in%20Gujarat%