S)%20arrested%20them%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20October%2018%2C%20based%20on%20the%20examination%20and%20data%20extraction%20from%20electronic%20devices%20seized%20from%20them%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ATS%20claimed%20it%20found%20letters%20and%20literature%20from%20their%20electronic%20devices%20that%20were%20linked%20to%20the%20banned%20Maoist%20outfit%20People%E2%80%99s%20Liberation%20Guerilla%20Army%20(PLGA)%20and%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Maoist).%20The%20documents%20were%20related%20to%20these%20outfits%20building%20a%20strong%20party%20and%20organisation%20for%20resistance%20against%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ATS%20says%20it%20arrested%20activist%20Brijesh%20Kushwaha%2C%2043%2C%20from%20his%20native%20place%20in%20Deoria%20while%20his%20wife%20Prabha%2C%2038%2C%20was%20arrested%20from%20her%20maternal%20house%20in%20Raipur%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%20Prabha%E2%80%99s%20family%20sources%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20she%20was%20three%20months%20pregnant%20and%20had%20gone%20to%20Raipur%20to%20spend%20time%20with%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20questioning%20the%20couple%20in%20July%202019%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20lodged%20against%20them%20on%20their%20alleged%20Naxal%20links%2C%20the%20ATS%20had%20seized%20their%20electronic%20devices%20and%20sent%20them%20for%20examination%20and%20data%20extraction%20to%20a%20forensic%20science%20laboratory%20(FSL).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ATS%20says%20it%20found%20documents%20linked%20to%20Naxals%20after%20carrying%20out%20an%20%E2%80%9Cintensive%20analysis%20of%20the%20report%20packed%20with%20the%20complete%20extracted%20digital%20data%20received%20from%20the%20FSL%20this%20month.%E2%80%9D%20The%20ATS%20also%20claims%20it%20recovered%20letters%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccomrades%20of%20CPI%20(Maoist)%2C%E2%80%9D%20with%20references%20to%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%20activities%E2%80%9D%20from%20their%20electronic%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20accused%20Kushwaha%20and%20Prabha%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%20activities%E2%80%9D%20and%20spreading%20Communist%20ideology%20through%20the%20outfits%20run%20by%20them.%20While%20Brijesh%20is%20linked%20to%20the%20Mazdoor%20Kisan%20Ekta%20Manch%20of%C2%A0Deoria%2C%20Prabha%20is%20connected%20with%20the%20outfit%20Savitri%20Bai%20Phule%20Sangarsh%20Samiti.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKushwaha%20completed%20his%20masters%20in%20Sanskrit%20from%20Deoria%20and%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20Inquilabi%20Chhatra%20Sabha%20during%20his%20student%20days.%20He%20met%20Prabha%20while%20working%20in%20Bilaspur%20in%202006%2C%20and%20they%20got%20married%20in%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20when%20the%20ATS%20had%20raided%20their%20home%20in%202019%20and%20questioned%20them%2C%20it%20did%20not%20find%20any%20%E2%80%9Ccredible%20material%20evidence%E2%80%9D%20due%20to%20which%20they%20were%20not%20arrested%2C%20said%20the%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202019%2C%20the%20UP%20ATS%20had%20lodged%20an%20FIR%20under%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20Sections%20121%20A%20and%20120%20B%20against%20seven%20people%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20were%20political%20and%20social%20activists.%20According%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20seen%2C%20the%20police%20said%20suspected%20Naxalites%20had%20been%20holding%20meetings%20in%20UP%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20were%20engaging%20in%20criminal%20conspiracy%20to%20instigate%20people%20for%20armed%20rebellion%20and%20making%20a%20plan%20for%20%3Cem%3Esatta%20parivartan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(change%20in%20government).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20time%2C%20the%20ATS%20had%20arrested%20two%20of%20the%20seven%20individuals%20mentioned%20in%20the%20FIR%20%E2%80%93%20Manish%20Azad%20aka%20Manish%20Srivastava%20and%20his%20wife%20Anita%20Srivastava%20%E2%80%93%20from%20their%20residence%20in%20Bhopal.%20Both%20of%20them%20have%20a%20background%20in%20translation%20and%20academic%20work.%20They%20were%20later%20granted%20bail%20in%20this%20case.%20Kushwaha%20and%20his%20wife%20were%20also%20named%20in%20this%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20conducted%20raids%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20Kanpur%2C%20Deoria%2C%20and%20Kushinagar%2C%20and%20seized%20several%20electronic%20devices%20and%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20questioned%20Kushwaha%20and%20Prabha%2C%20they%20were%20not%20arrested%20in%202019%2C%20as%20earlier%20mentioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20arresting%20the%20couple%20on%20October%2018%2C%20police%20said%20they%20were%20also%20searching%20their%20residences.%20Prabha%20would%20be%20taken%20to%20Lucknow%20on%20a%20transit%20remand%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20had%20recently%20interrogated%20one%20of%20the%20co-accused%20in%20the%202019%20FIR%2C%20Manish%20Azad%2C%20as%20it%20conducted%20simultaneous%20searches%20at%20the%20residences%20and%20offices%20of%20several%20activists%2C%20including%20Manish%E2%80%99s%20sister%20and%20national%20secretary%20of%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Union%20for%20Civil%20Liberties%2C%20Seema%20Azad%2C%20and%20students%20in%20various%20cities%20of%20eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20NIA%20said%20its%20raid%20was%20against%20the%20suspects%20in%20connection%20with%20alleged%20attempts%20by%20leaders%20and%20cadres%20of%20the%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20to%20revive%20the%20banned%20organisation%20across%20UP.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697638821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18194314%2Fimage-1403.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fup-four-years-after-seizing-electronic-devices-ats-arrests-activist-couple-for-alleged-naxal-links%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ATS%20arrested%20Brijesh%20Kushwaha%20and%20his%20wife%20Prabha%2C%20claiming%20that%2