for%20them%20to%20attend%20classes%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kumari.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndoctrinated%20to%20hate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20abandoned%20temple%20in%20Palia%20Kalan%2C%20Janaki%20Devi%2C%20a%20priestess%2C%20has%20been%20asking%20Hindus%20to%20re-establish%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20temple%20by%20joining%20her%20in%20praying%20to%20deities%20and%20acting%20upon%20what%20Hinduism%20truly%20advocates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20came%20here%2C%20this%20temple%20had%20evil%20spirits.%20I%20cleansed%20the%20temple%20and%20now%20it%20has%20become%20a%20%3Cem%3EDharamshala%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20the%20needy%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Devi.%20She%20also%20adds%20that%20ill%20persons%20who%20stay%20at%20the%20temple%20magically%20heal%20after%20chanting%20%3Cem%3Emantras%3C%2Fem%3E.%20While%20Devi%20is%20not%20associated%20with%20the%20RSS%20or%20EVF%2C%20she%20subscribes%20to%20the%20ideology%20of%20Hindutva%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18164305%2FEV4-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18164305%2FEV4-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18164305%2FEV4-1-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18164305%2FEV4-1-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680669%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPriestess%20Janaki%20Devi%20at%20the%20temple%20in%20Palia%20Kalan.%20Photo%3A%20Tarushi%20Aswani%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EDevi%20fully%20echoes%20the%20idea%20that%20Ekal%20advocates%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20more%20training.%20The%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20should%20also%20train%20women%20to%20defend%20themselves%20and%20fight%20against%20those%20corrupting%20Hindu%20minds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CHindutva%20ko%20aage%20badhaane%20ke%20liye%20prayaas%20karna%20padhega%2C%20yahan%20buhot%20log%20issai%20dharam%20mein%20jaa%20rhay%20hain.%20Humein%20yeh%20rokna%20hoga.%20Chahe%20granth%20ki%20padhaai%20ho%20yaan%20danda%20chalana%2C%20Hinduon%20ko%20sab%20aana%20chahiye%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Hindus%20have%20to%20put%20up%20with%20struggle%20to%20move%20forward.%20Several%20people%20here%20are%20converting%20to%20Christianity.%20We%20have%20to%20stop%20this.%20Whether%20it%20is%20through%20reading%20Hindu%20scriptures%20or%20through%20force.%20Hindus%20should%20know%20everything)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Devi%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20propagating%20Hindutva%2C%20Devi%20undertakes%20a%20%E2%80%98noble%E2%80%99%20task%20every%20Friday.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20disciples%20and%20I%20make%20sure%20to%20blast%20%3Cem%3Ebhajans%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20full%20volume%20when%20they%20(Muslims)%20read%20%3Cem%3Eazaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20Friday%20namaz.%20This%20is%20my%20way%20to%20stop%20Islam.%20But%20Christians%20are%20out%20of%20control%2C%20they%20give%20money%2C%20property%2C%20and%20alcohol%20to%20convert%20Hindus%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Devi.%20%E2%80%9CSanatanis%20are%20precious%2C%20they%20should%20be%20trained%20by%20the%20Sangh.%20They%20are%20the%20true%20fighters%20in%20the%20cause.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKumari%20and%20Rana%20agree%20with%20Devi.%20They%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20this%20%E2%80%98training%E2%80%99%20that%20Devi%20suggests%20is%20needed%20to%20keep%20the%20population%20of%20Christians%20and%20Muslims%20under%20check.%20They%20regularly%20consult%20Devi%20and%20take%20her%20suggestions%20to%20the%20local%20RSS%20affiliates%20who%20also%20contact%20Devi%20frequently%20concerning%20mass%20conversion%20conspiracies%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMuslims%20on%20the%20Indo-Nepal%20border%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20met%20with%20Mahender%20Yadav%2C%20the%20supervisor%20of%20Ekal%20schools%20in%20Sitapur%20district.%20Yadav%2C%20who%20took%20Kumari%20and%20Rana%20under%20his%20wings%2C%20believes%20that%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20%E2%80%9Cneed%20to%20be%20shown%20their%20rightful%20place%20in%20society%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20can%20either%20accept%20Hindu%20supremacy%20or%20convert%20to%20Hinduism.%20Ekal%20prepares%20children%20to%20identify%20enemies%20of%20Hinduism%20at%20an%20early%20stage%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20Yadav%2C%20430%20Ekal%20schools%20and%20institutions%20further%20the%20agenda%20of%20radicalising%20students.%20But%20the%20propaganda%20that%20these%20schools%20further%20through%20Tharus%20travels%20beyond%20classrooms.%20Due%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20these%20schools%2C%20Muslims%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20villages%20that%20border%20Nepal%20feel%20vulnerable%20with%20children%20being%20indoctrinated%20to%20hate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBrij%20Bihari%2C%20a%20social%20activist%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Sitapur%20district%2C%20feels%20that%20Tharus%20are%20being%20%E2%80%9Cused%20as%20foot%20soldiers%20in%20the%20border%20districts%20to%20channelise%20Hindutva%20sentiment%E2%80%9D.%20Bihari%20also%20views%20this%20as%20a%20dangerous%20trend%20which%20could%20jeopardise%20the%20lives%20of%20Christians%20and%20Muslims%20along%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20new%20schools%20of%20%E2%80%98hate%E2%80%99%20coming%20up%20every%20day%2C%20Muslims%20like%20advocate%20Pervez%20Iqbal%20feel%20that%20his%20community%20is%20staring%20at%20genocide.%20Iqbal%2C%20who%20is%20a%20local%20activist%20from%20Shravasti%2C%20feels%20that%20Hindutva%20groups%20are%20gaining%20stronger%20ground%20in%20the%20border%20districts%20ever%20since%202014%2C%20and%20even%20more%20since%202019%20%E2%80%93%20coinciding%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIqbal%E2%80%99s%20neighbour%2C%20a%2060-year-old%20Muslim%20man%2C%20Rabiullah%2C%20feels%20that%20with%20tribals%20siding%20with%20Hindutva%20groups%2C%20Muslims%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20leave%20their%20homes%20merely%20for%20being%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CYeh%20log%20kabhi%20bhi%20nikaal%20denge%20humein%2C%20phir%20itni%20mehnat%20ka%20ghar%20do%20paise%20mein%20bech%20kar%20bhaagna%20parhega%2C%20yahan%20haalaat%20waisay%20bhi%20election%20ke%20time%20buhot%20garam%20rehte%20hain%3C%2Fem%3E%20(These%20people%20can%20kick%20us%20out%20any%20moment.%20We%20will%20have%20to%20sell%20our%20hard-earned%20homes%20in%20distress%20and%20migrate.%20As%20it%20is%2C%20during%20election%20time%2C%20the%20situation%20is%20hot%20to%20handle%20here)%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rabiullah%2C%20who%20has%20lived%20in%20Shravasti%20all%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697631611000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18164010%2FThe-Wire-44.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Findo-nepal-border-schools-hindutva-outfit-indoctrinate%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Ekal%20Vidyalaya%20Foundation%2C%20which%20is%20linked%20to%20RSS%20and%20VHP%2C%20is%20indoctrinating%20women%20and%20children%20of%20a%20the%20Tharu%20tribal%20community.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Findo-nepal-border-schools-hindutva-outfit-indoctrinate%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Power%20Bills%20Rising%20While%20Adani%20Takes%20Money%20from%20India's%20Poorest%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18164052%2FUntitled-design-2-3.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Congress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20on%20Wednesday%20(October%2018)%20accused%20the%20Adani%20group%20of%20over-invoicing%20coal%20prices%20and%20taking%20money%20out%20of%20the%20pockets%20of%20poor%20people%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Gandhi%20cited%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-coal-imports-over-pricing-customers-overcharged-fuel-ft%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eby%20London-based%20financial%20daily%2C%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ETimes%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20had%20in%20a%20detailed%20investigation%20last%20week%2C%20titled%2C%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F7aadb3d7-4a03-44ba-a01e-8ddd8bce29ed%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20mystery%20of%20the%20Adani%20coal%20imports%20that%20quietly%20doubled%20in%20value%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20found%20that%20Adani%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20country%E2%80%99s%20largest%20private%20coal%20importer%2C%20has%20been%20inflating%20fuel%20costs%E2%80%9D%20leading%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmillions%20of%20Indian%20consumers%20and%20businesses%20overpaying%20for%20electricity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20story%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ETimes%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20pre-eminent%20financial%20newspapers%20in%20the%20world%2C%20where%20they%20are%20clearly%20stating%20that%20%E2%80%9CAdani%20and%20the%20mysterious%20coal%20price%20rises%E2%80%9D.%20Mr.%20Adani%20buys%20coal%20in%20Indonesia%20and%20by%20the%20time%20coal%20arrives%20in%20India%2C%20its%20prices%20doubles%20and%20he%20has%20taken%20approximately%20Rs%2012%2C000%20crores%20from%20the%20pockets%20of%20the%20poorest%20people%20in%20India.%20Our%20electricity%20prices%20are%20going%20up%20and%20Adani%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20over-invoicing%20while%20taking%20money%20from%20the%20pockets%20of%20the%20poorest%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20said%20that%20while%20the%20%3Cem%3EFT%3C%2Fem%3E%20story%20would%20%E2%80%9Cbring%20down%20any%20government%E2%80%9D%2C%20Indian%20media%20has%20not%20picked%20up%20the%20story.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CInteresting%20question%20to%20me%E2%80%A6the%3Cem%3E%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20a%20huge%20story.%20This%20story%20would%20bring%20down%20any%20government.%20This%20is%20direct%20theft%20by%20a%20man%2C%20who%20has%20been%20protected%20again%2C%20and%20again%2C%20and%20again%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India.%20And%20the%20surprising%20thing%20is%2C%20not%20a%20single%20Indian%20newspaper%20is%20interested%20in%20picking%20up%20the%20story%2C%20not%20a%20single%20media%20channel%20is%20interested%20in%20picking%20up%20the%20story%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20giving%20electricity%20subsidies%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20going%20to%20do%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20while%20we%20are%20giving%20electricity%20subsidies%2C%20Mr.%20Adani%20is%20over%20invoicing%20coal%20and%20stealing%20directly%20from%20the%20people%20of%20India%2C%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20understand%20why%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20comment%20on%20this.%20This%20cannot%20happen%20without%20the%20protection%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India.%20It%20is%20impossible.%20So%2C%20the%20question%20is%3A%20why%20is%20there%20no%20action%20being%20taken%20on%20this%20gentleman%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Will%20definitely%20get%20it%20done%2C%20why%20not%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20in%20January%2C%20US%20short-seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%E2%80%99s%20report%20alleged%20stock%20market%20manipulation%20by%20the%20Adani%20group%20and%20also%20raised%20questions%20about%20regulatory%20mechanisms%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStock%20market%20watchdog%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20came%20under%20fire%20even%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20expert%20committee%20pointed%20to%20certain%20changes%20in%20rules%20that%20may%20have%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20Adani%20to%20escape%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Adani%20group%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Flatest%2Fcorporate%2Fstory%2Fadani-group-hits-out-at-financial-times-for-trying-to-tarnish-reputation-financially-destabilise-company-401342-2023-10-10%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edenied%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20charges%20and%20said%20it%20has%20been%20vindicated%20by%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20(DRI%E2%80%99s)%20decision%20this%20year%20to%20withdraw%20an%20appeal%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20a%20case%20against%20one%20of%20the%2040%20importers%20named%20in%202016.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20issue%20of%20overvaluation%20in%20the%20import%20of%20coal%20was%20conclusively%20settled%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20highest%20court%20of%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20the%20Congress%20party%20party%20will%20initiate%20a%20probe%20against%20the%20Adani%20group%20if%20voted%20to%20power%20next%20year%2C%20Gandhi%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWill%20definitely%20get%20it%20done%2C%20why%20not%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CLook%2C%20this%20is%20not%20about%20Adani%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20this%20Rs%2032%2C000%20crore%20has%20been%20stolen%20from%20the%20people%20of%20India%2C%20that%20is%20the%20issue%20and%20whoever%20steals%20Rs%2032%2C000%20crore%20will%20be%20investigated%2C%20why%20not%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResponding%20