0amid%20an%20online%20meeting%20of%20senior%20officers%20on%20Tuesday%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20unable%20to%20independently%20confirm%20if%20CAG%20has%20withdrawn%20its%20proposal%20%E2%80%9Cto%20halt%20audits%20in%20union%20ministries%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98performance%20audit%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20CAG%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcag.gov.in%2Fen%2Ffaqs%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20performance%20audit%20%E2%80%9Cfocuses%20on%20whether%20interventions%2C%20programmes%20and%20institutions%20are%20performing%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20principles%20of%20economy%2C%20efficiency%20and%20effectiveness%20and%20whether%20there%20is%20room%20for%20improvement.%20Performance%20is%20examined%20against%20suitable%20criteria%20and%20the%20causes%20of%20deviations%20from%20those%20criteria%20or%20other%20problems%20are%20analysed.%20The%20aim%20is%20to%20answer%20key%20audit%20questions%20and%20to%20provide%20recommendations%20for%20improvement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20website%20also%20states%20that%20a%20compliance%20audit%20%E2%80%9Cfocuses%20on%20whether%20a%20particular%20subject%20matter%20is%20in%20compliance%20with%20the%20criteria.%20Compliance%20auditing%20is%20performed%20by%20assessing%20whether%20activities%2C%20financial%20transactions%20and%20information%20are%2C%20in%20all%20material%20aspects%2C%20in%20compliance%20with%20the%20applicable%20authorities%20which%20include%20the%20Constitution%2C%20Acts%2C%20Laws%2C%20rules%20and%20regulations%2C%20budgetary%20resolutions%2C%20policy%2C%20contracts%2C%20agreements%2C%20established%20codes%2C%20sanctions%2C%20supply%20orders%2C%20agreed%20terms%20or%20the%20general%20principles%20governing%20sound%20public%20sector%20financial%20management%20and%20the%20conduct%20of%20public%20officials.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcag.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fjournal%2Fjanuary-2015%2Ftypes_of_audit.html%5C%22%3EThematic%20audits%3C%2Fa%3E%20refer%20to%20audits%20which%20may%20have%20both%20compliance%20and%20performance%20audit%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECAG%20reports%20have%20been%20of%20special%20interest%20after%20the%20UPA%20government%20came%20under%20fire%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2F2g-accused-acquitted-happened-scam-wasnt%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9C2G%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcoalgate-scam-ex-coal-secretary-h-c-gupta-sentenced-to-three-years-in-jail%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Ccoal%20block%20allocation%20scam%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20which%20were%20revealed%20when%20Vinod%20Rai%20was%20the%20CAG%2C%20and%20which%20had%20serious%20consequences%20on%20the%20UPA%E2%80%99s%20credibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwelve%20key%20CAG%20reports%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwelve%20key%20audit%20reports%20were%20presented%20in%20parliament%20during%20the%20monsoon%20session%20that%20ended%20on%20August%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%2012%20CAG%20reports%20revealed%20corruption%20and%20irregularities%20in%20the%20functioning%20of%20several%20Union%20government%20ministries%20and%20departments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20included%20the%20CAG%20reports%20on%20the%20irregularities%20in%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20and%20the%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20project%20that%20were%20in%20particular%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20opposition%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20including%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20%E2%80%93%20who%20accused%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20of%20presiding%20over%20%E2%80%9Cscams%E2%80%9D%2C%20demanding%20accountability%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereported%20that%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20October%2C%20there%20were%20%E2%80%9Cverbal%20orders%E2%80%9D%20passed%20in%20the%20CAG%20office%20in%20New%20Delhi%20to%20%E2%80%9Cstop%20all%20field%20work%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0Officers%20then%20asked%20for%20written%20orders%2C%20in%20order%20to%20be%20able%20to%20pass%20them%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20field%20work%20is%20vital%20for%20the%20auditing%20of%20ministries%20and%20departments%20%E2%80%93%20that%20eventually%20results%20in%20reports%20put%20out%20by%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20official%20audit%20body%20and%20helps%20in%20establishing%20accountability%20and%20checks%20on%20government%20spending%20and%20finances.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ealso%20reported%20that%20CAG%20Girish%20Chandra%20Murmu%20is%20said%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20signing%20any%20report%E2%80%9D%20that%20necessarily%20needs%20to%20bear%20his%20signature%2C%20along%20with%20that%20of%20the%20officer-in-charge%2C%20invariably%20an%20officer%20of%20the%20Indian%20Audit%20and%20Accounts%20Service%20(IA%26amp%3BAS).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20release%20on%20October%2013%2C%20the%20CAG%20office%20%E2%80%9Crejected%E2%80%9D%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECalling%20itself%20the%20Supreme%20Audit%20Institution%20of%20India%20(SAI)%2C%20it%20said%20CAG%20%E2%80%9Cis%20committed%20to%20fulfilling%20its%20mandate%20of%20ensuring%20transparency%20and%20accountability%20in%20governance%3B%20and%20is%20confident%20of%20surpassing%20previous%20years%E2%80%99%20output.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20would%20not%20be%20possible%20if%20there%20was%20even%20the%20slightest%20truth%20in%20the%20alleged%20contention%20that%20field%20audit%20has%20been%20suspended.%20Rest%20assured%2C%20field%20audit%20continues%20full%20force%2C%20suitably%20buttressed%20by%20data%20analytics%20and%20digital%20audit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehad%20also%20reported%20that%20the%20verbal%20orders%20came%20close%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fofficers-cag-reports-ayushman-bharat-bharatmala-transferred%5C%22%3Etransfers%20of%20three%20officers%20who%20were%20in%20charge%20of%20audit%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20exposed%20corruption%20in%20the%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20project%20and%20Ayushman%20Bharat.%20A%20third%20officer%20who%20had%20initiated%20the%20audit%20of%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20report%20was%20also%20transferred.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3Es%20report%2C%20opposition%20parties%20including%20the%20Congress%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcag-officers-transfers-opposition-accuses-modi-government-intimidation%5C%22%3Eaccused%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20BJP%20government%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccorruption%E2%80%9D%20and%20intimidation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%E2%80%99s%20October%2013%20press%20release%20had%20also%20refuted%20that%20the%20transfers%20had%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20the%20audit%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20set%20the%20record%20straight%2C%20matters%20of%20transfer%20and%20postings%20are%20a%20matter%20of%20administrative%20convenience%20and%20to%20read%20ulterior%20motives%20into%20these%20is%20highly%20presumptuous%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20had%20said%20in%20the%20same%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697627672000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F10231629%2Fgc-murmu.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmystery-over-maharashtra-accountant-general-issuing-note-stopping-performance-audit-field-work-cag-again-denies-orders-sent%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20order%20issued%20by%20the%20Accountant%20General%20(Accounts%20And%20Entitlements)%20-%20I%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Mumbai%20(Pradhan%20Mahalekhakar%20Ka%20Karyalay%20(Lekhapariksha)%20-1%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Mumbai)%20dated%20October%209%20accessed%20by%20The%20Wire%20stated%20that%20all%20