201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680657%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22828%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Munshiganj%20pandal%2C%20being%20organised%20by%20Muslims%20and%20Hindus.%20Photo%3A%20Joydeep%20Sarkar%2FThe%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20festival%20for%20all%20of%20us.%20We%20all%20live%20here.%20Ram%20Pal%2C%20our%20local%20potter%20makes%20the%20idol.%20Joy%20and%20Bikash%20look%20after%20the%20ritual%20part.%20Everyone%20in%20the%20mohalla%20contributes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3ESex%20workers%20in%20the%20locality%20send%20donations.%20But%20they%20do%20not%20take%20part%20in%20the%20puja%20despite%20our%20requests%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mohammad%20Latif%2C%20a%20key%20organiser.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWho%20will%20we%20press%20for%20money%3F%20Whatever%20people%20give%2C%20we%20collect%20that%20and%20organise%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20committee%20has%20struggled%20to%20collect%20Rs%201%2C30%2C000.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20grant%20of%20Rs%2070%2C000%20to%20each%20puja%20committee%20has%20helped%2C%20they%20said.%20The%20organisers%20gift%20clothes%20to%20the%20poor%20and%20also%20organise%20lunches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20Hindu%2C%20but%20festivals%20like%20Eid%20and%20Muharram%20are%20just%20as%20much%20a%20part%20of%20my%20celebrations.%20My%20entire%20family%20takes%20part%20in%20these%20events%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Bikas%20Roy%2C%20one%20of%20the%20organisers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20amalgamation%20of%20cultures%20has%20fostered%20a%20strong%20sense%20of%20togetherness%20in%20the%20neighbourhood.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuslim%20women%20also%20participate%20in%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Esindoor%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Ekhela%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%99%20smearing%20each%20other%20with%20vermillion%20on%20Bijoya%20Dashami.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Translated%20from%20the%20Bengali%20original%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697626134000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161403%2FScreenshot-2023-10-18-at-4.13.45%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fram-temple-ayodhya-khidirpur-muslims-durga-puja%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20Munshiganj%20in%20Khidirpur%2C%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20in%20a%20modest%20neighbourhood%20are%20worried.%20Their%20concerns%20centre%20around%20unfinished%20pandals%20and%20financial%20constraints%20for%20the%20common%20community%20puja%20they%20organise.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fram-temple-ayodhya-khidirpur-muslims-durga-puja%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ahmedabad%20and%20the%20Art%20of%20Weaponising%20an%20India-Pakistan%20Spectacle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18151955%2FF8aL8TQaAAAtZFh.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EEntering%20the%20stands%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20in%20Ahmedabad%20from%20either%20end%20can%20be%20a%20tad%20bit%20haunting%20for%20the%20uninitiated.%20An%20unforgivingly%20vast%20sea%20of%20orange%20stares%20deep%20into%20your%20soul%2C%20almost%20as%20a%20reminder%20of%20whose%20city%20you%E2%80%99re%20in%2C%20lest%20you%20forget.%20The%20choice%20of%20colour%20for%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20seating%20area%20isn%E2%80%99t%20incidental%20here.%20It%20very%20firmly%20delivers%20an%20unsubtle%2C%20unmasked%20and%20politically%20charged%20message%20%E2%80%93%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20reason%20this%20place%20is%20named%20after%20a%20certain%20someone%20and%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20de%20facto%20power%20centre%20of%20Indian%20cricket%20now%20being%20run%20by%20another%20certain%20someone%E2%80%99s%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20legend%20of%20this%20stadium%20is%20built%20around%20its%20capacity%20to%20host%20more%20than%20100%2C000%20people%20%E2%80%93%20the%20exact%20number%20varies%20by%20different%20accounts%20but%20exceeds%20130%2C000%20on%20the%20upside.%20By%20every%20verifiable%20account%20though%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20indeed%20the%20biggest%20cricket%20stadium%20in%20the%20world%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20capacity%20was%20never%20the%20only%20factor%20for%20this%20venue%20to%20be%20the%20obvious%20choice%20to%20host%20the%20lip-smacking%20India-Pakistan%20game%20at%20the%20ongoing%20Cricket%20World%20Cup.%20There%E2%80%99s%20so%20much%20to%20leverage%20out%20of%20staging%20this%20spectacle%20at%20a%20stadium%20that%E2%80%99s%20fast%20becoming%20a%20manifestation%20for%20the%20personality%20cult%20of%20the%20leader%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20built%20in%20service%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENarendra%20Modi%20is%20an%20incredibly%20popular%20leader%20in%20most%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20today%20but%20there%E2%80%99s%20perhaps%20no%20place%20but%20Ahmedabad%20that%20he%20can%20entirely%20count%20on%20to%20deliver%20to%20perfection%20everything%20that%20he%20needs.%20The%20waters%20had%20already%20been%20tested%20earlier%20this%20year%20when%20Australian%20Prime%20Minister%20Anthony%20Albanese%20had%20been%20invited%20at%20this%20venue%20on%20March%209%20before%20the%20start%20of%20an%20India-Australia%20test%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPacking%20the%20stands%20for%20test%20cricket%20in%20India%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20easiest%20of%20jobs.%20To%20stage%20a%20political%20event%20that%20looks%20nothing%20short%20of%20a%20music%20concert%20required%20not%20only%20for%20the%20stands%20to%20look%20reasonably%20full%20but%20also%20for%20the%20crowd%20to%20uniformly%20act%20obsequious%20and%20indebted%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20their%20leader.%20Individually%20vetting%20the%20thousands%20you%E2%80%99ve%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesnownews.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Frevealed-why-tickets-for-day-1-of-4th-ind-aus-test-in-ahmedabad-are-locked-out-leaving-fans-disheartened-article-98405395%5C%22%3Edistributed%20free%20tickets%3C%2Fa%3E%20amongst%20is%20impossible%2C%20even%20for%20a%20party%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20resources.%20The%20safer%20option%20is%20to%20stage%20it%20among%20a%20people%20you%20have%20complete%20confidence%20in%20to%20not%20spoil%20your%20script.%20This%20is%20where%20Ahmedabad%20can%20be%20blindly%20banked%20upon%20to%20deliver.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20deliver%20Ahmedabad%20did%2C%20to%20perfection%2C%20as%20Modi%20and%20Albanese%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-australian-pm-anthony-albanese-to-watch-india-australia-test-in-gujarat-today-3845277%5C%22%3Erode%20on%20a%20chariot%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20the%20ground%20taking%20a%20lap%20of%20honour%20to%20rapturous%20reception%20of%20a%20crowd%20(far%20from%20capacity%20despite%20the%20best%20efforts)%20just%20too%20grateful%20to%20be%20breathing%20the%20same%20air%20the%20man%20they%E2%80%99ve%20submitted%20their%20ability%20to%20reason%20for%20did.%20It%20was%20pretty%20emblematic%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98new%20India%E2%80%99%20where%20staged%20events%20with%20vetted%20audience%20in%20attendance%20inflating%20the%20ego%20of%20an%20elected%20leader%20is%20how%20national%20pride%20is%20measured.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECricket%20has%20willingly%20allowed%20itself%20to%20be%20used%20as%20a%20vehicle%20facilitating%20this%20pomposity%20and%20the%20gigantic%20bowl%20in%20Ahmedabad%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20this%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Cricket%20World%20Cup%3A%20The%20Good%20and%20the%20Ugly%20of%20a%20Hysterical%20Crowd%E2%80%99s%20Collective%20Energy%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-world-cup-hysterical-crowd-collective-energy%5C%22%3ECricket%20World%20Cup%3A%20The%20Good%20and%20the%20Ugly%20of%20a%20Hysterical%20Crowd%E2%80%99s%20Collective%20Energy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%20when%20India%20hosted%20Pakistan%20at%20this%20stadium%20though%2C%20the%20vast%20sea%20of%20orange%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20meant%20to%20be%20as%20conspicuous%20as%20it%20looked%20on%20the%20drone%20shots.%20Much%20of%20the%20sitting%20area%2C%20already%20expected%20to%20have%20turned%20blue%20by%20the%20time%20of%20toss%2C%20remained%20unoccupied%20well%20past%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20stands%20eventually%20did%20fill%20considerably%2C%20though%20the%20broadcasters%20refrained%20from%20repeatedly%20boasting%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98record%20number%E2%80%99%20of%20people%20gathered%20for%20a%20cricket%20match.%20Which%20is%20probably%20an%20indication%20the%20number%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20the%20one%20they%20were%20desperately%20craving%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20anticipation%20built%20around%20this%20game%20was%20somewhat%20rooted%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%20long%20time%2C%20Pakistan%20attempted%20some%20rabble-rousing.%20Both%20the%20cricket%20boards%20have%20been%20at%20diplomatic%20loggerheads%20for%20a%20while%20now.%20India%E2%80%99s%20steadfast%20refusal%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20didn%E2%80%99t%20change%20during%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20last%20month%20and%20that%20left%20the%20hosts%20justifiably%20aggrieved.%20Having%20to%20come%20across%20as%20not%20taking%20things%20lying%20down%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20had%20at%20one%20point%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fstory%2Fpakistan-wont-play-world-cup-if-india-do-not-come-for-asia-cup-pcb-chief-2301883-2022-11-26%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520Short%26amp%3Btext%3DPakistan%2520Cricket%2520Board%2520(PCB)%2520chief%2Cover%2520World%2520Cup%2520next%2520year.%5C%22%3Ethreatened%20to%20reciprocate%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20not%20showing%20up%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%20but%20few%20treated%20it%20with%20any%20seriousness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%E2%80%99s%20official%20position%20is%20to%20not%20extend%20cricketing%20relations%20with%20Pakistan%20beyond%20multilateral%20tournaments.%20The%20board%20of%20course%20does%20not%20have%20the%20autonomy%20to%20decide%20this%20on%20its%20own%20and%20must%20adhere%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20directives.%20But%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20element%20of%20subterfuge%20here%3B%20in%20that%2C%20the%20BCCI%20likes%20to%20pose%20as%20if%20it%20plays%20Pakistan%20in%20these%20international%20events%20only%20out%20of%20fulfilling%20its%20commitment%20despite%20the%20strongest%20reservations.%20But%20this%20could%20not%20be%20further%20from%20the%20truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20it%20has%20affirmed%20a%20very%20uncompromising%20and%20principled%20stand%2C%20when%20it%20actually%20comes%20to%20milking%20the%20popularity%20of%20an%20India-Pakistan%20match%2C%20the%20BCCI%20and%20its%20entire%20ecosystem%20that%20feeds%20off%20cricket%20cares%20little%20about%20those%20principles.%20Tournament%20after%20tournament%2C%20formats%20and%20schedules%20are%20rigged%20to%20maximise%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20two%20teams%20facing%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20home%20broadcasters%20in%20India%20have%20no%20hesitation%20building%20up%20the%20game%20as%20the%20ultimate%20cultural%20marker%20of%20an%20entire%20nation.%20A%20slew%20of%20news%20anchors%20and%20former%20cricketers%20who%E2%80%99ve%20carved%20a%20brand%20out%20of%20insincerely%20rehashing%20hawkish%20jargon%20on%20TV%20are%20all%20too%20happy%20to%20be%20sharing%20screen-space%20with%20their%20Pakistani%20counterparts.%20And%20then%20follows%20the%20same%20tired%20rhetoric%20of%20sports%20having%20to%20rise%20above%20the%20ugliness%20of%20daily%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20BCCI%20ascribes%20a%20first-among-equals%20status%20to%20an%20India-Pakistan%20contest%20was%20confirmed%20during%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20itself%20when%20a%20special%20reserve%20day%20was%20arranged%20for%20it%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20washout.%20None%20of%20the%20other%20teams%20had%20their%20games%20insured%20by%20such%20an%20arrangement%20and%20worse%20still%2C%20they%20were%20made%20to%20publicly%20state%20they%20were%20on%20board%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20special%20treatment%20for%20this%20fixture%20only%20became%20more%20blatant%20on%20Saturday%20when%20a%20haphazardly%20organised%20pre-game%20entertainment%20show%20was%20arranged%20ahead%20of%20the%20match.%C2%A0%20Featuring%20some%20of%20the%20more%20famous%20names%20in%20the%20Indian%20music%20industry%2C%20the%20show%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20the%20perfect%20precursor%20before%20the%20showdown%20event%20in%20front%20of%20a%20record%20crowd.%20It%E2%80%99s%20hard%20to%20think%20of%20another%20world%20event%20across%20all%20sports%20that%20commences%20without%20an%20opening%20ceremony%20but%20then%20has%20one%20specially%20arranged%20for%20a%20blockbuster%20game%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20it%20was%20the%20backlash%20they%20faced%20for%20this%20brazenness%20or%20maybe%20it%20was%20a%20case%20of%20poor%20due%20diligence%20where%20someone%20forgot%20to%20clarify%20who%20pays%20royalty%20fees%20to%20the%20music%20labels%2C%20but%20minutes%20after%2C%20yes%2C%20%3Cem%3Eafter%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20show%20began%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20only%20for%20the%20live%20audience%20in%20the%20stadium%20and%20that%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20televised.%20Nothing%20could%E2%80%99ve%20summed%20up%20the%20BCCI%E2%80%99s%20ineptitude%2C%20chicanery%2C%20and%20all-round%20clumsiness%20more%20poetically.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20tournament%20is%20wide%20open%20still%20and%20odds%20aren%E2%80%99t%20totally%20stacked%20against%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20locking%20a%20faceoff%20in%20the%20final%20at%20the%20same%20venue.%20Who%20knows%2C%20it%20might%20even%20prompt%20the%20BCCI%20into%20arranging%20a%20closing%20ceremony%20for%20the%20tournament%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShould%20it%20really%20materialise%20though%2C%20no%20one%20is%20going%20to%20be%20happier%20than%20the%20BCCI.%20The%20political%20imagery%20of%20India%20defeating%20Pakistan%20to%20lift%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20ultimate%20prize%20in%20a%20stadium%20named%20after%20%E2%80%93%20and%20perhaps%20even%20in%20presence%20of%20%E2%80%93%20its%20tallest%20active%20politician%20is%20massive%3B%20particularly%20six%20months%20before%20the%20country%20goes%20to%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20India%20lifted%20a%20World%20Cup%20at%20home%2C%20the%20visuals%20of%20a%20jampacked%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20in%20Mumbai%20jamming%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fshorts%2FGyhPAE58FR4%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EVande%20Matram%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20chorus%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20for%20a%20memory%20everyone%20went%20home%20with.%20The%20scenes%20might%20very%20well%20repeat%20in%20a%20month%E2%80%99s%20time%20but%20Ahmedabad%20may%20have%20a%20slightly%20different%20choice%20of%20song.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20stadium%20has%20in%20a%20short%20time%20managed%20to%20shift%20the%20fan%20culture%20to%20be%20more%20representative%20of%20the%20politics%20its%20benefactors%20stand%20for.%20Politically%20loaded%20religious%20sloganeering%20is%20getting%20increasingly%20common.%20The%20familiar%20%3Cem%3EBharat%20Mata%20Ki%20Jai%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3EVande%20Matram%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20now%20followed%20with%20the%20even%20more%20affirmatively%20raised%20%3Cem%3EJai%20Shri%20Ram.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20an%20innocuous%20invocation%20of%20faith.%20During%20the%20India-Australia%20test%20in%20March%2C%20the%20chants%20were%20directed%20at%20Indian%20fast%20bowler%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.india.com%2Fsports%2Ffans-chant-jai-shree-ram-in-front-of-mohammed-shami-during-4th-test-between-ind-aus-at-ahmedabad-video-goes-viral-watch-5938124%2F%5C%22%3EMohammed%20Shami%3C%2Fa%3E.%20No%20one%20chose%20to%20address%20it%20then%20and%20this%20time%20the%20Pakistani%20batsman%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket-news%2Findia-vs-pakistan-fans-taunt-muhammad-rizwan-with-jai-shri-ram-chants-politicians-call-it-unacceptable-11697362408544.html%5C%22%3EMohammad%20Rizwan%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20at%20the%20receiving%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22India-Pakistan%20Cricket%3A%20On%20a%20Sticky%20Wicket%20in%20Ahmedabad%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-pakistan-cricket-on-a-sticky-wicket-in-ahmedabad%5C%22%3EIndia-Pakistan%20Cricket%3A%20On%20a%20Sticky%20Wicket%20in%20Ahmedabad%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20back%2C%20former%20PCB%20chairman%20Najam%20Sethi%20had%20voiced%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fsports%2Fnajam-sethi-to-icc-bosses-pakistan-dont-want-to-play-in-ahmedabad-unless-they-are-in-wc-final%2Farticleshow%2F100823154.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Econcerns%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Ahmedabad%20being%20the%20proposed%20venue%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20for%20Pakistan%20to%20face%20India.%20The%20city%20indeed%20confirmed%20his%20worst%20fears.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%20home%20crowd%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20particularly%20cordial%20to%20a%20visiting%20team%2C%20let%20alone%20to%20the%20fiercest%20rival.%20Boorish%20and%20uncouth%20behaviour%20too%20is%20part%20of%20the%20deal%20and%20professionals%20are%20more%20than%20prepared%20for%20it.%20Chants%20aimed%20specifically%20at%20mocking%20a%20Muslim%20player%E2%80%99s%20faith%2C%20however%2C%20cannot%20pass%20as%20harmless%20banter%20and%20reflect%20worryingly%20of%20the%20rot%20building%20up%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20Indian%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20been%20deeply%20concerning%20if%20it%20was%20only%20limited%20to%20a%20few%20miscreants%20creating%20a%20menace.%20This%20shift%20in%20vibe%20instead%20was%20in%20all%20its%20glory%20as%20the%20DJ%20played%20a%20recently%20popular%20number%20from%20the%20film%20%3Cem%3EAdipurush%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20chants%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Fcricket%2Find-vs-pak-fans-sing-jai-shree-ram-at-narendra-modi-stadium-in-unison-makes-for-goosebumps-moment-watch-8617659.html%5C%22%3Ereverberated%20through%20every%20corner%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndian%20cricket%20has%20never%20militantly%20kept%20faith%20out%20of%20the%20stadium%20experience.%20Wankhede%20regulars%20famously%20raise%20%3Cem%3EGanpati%20Bappa%20Morya%3C%2Fem%3E%20every%20now%20and%20then%20but%20it%20has%20never%20been%20weaponised%20to%20intimidate%20players%20from%20another%20faith.%20The%20chant%20is%20in%20fact%20inclusive%20in%20nature%20and%20only%20invokes%20a%20feeling%20that%E2%80%99s%20distinctly%20associated%20with%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20happening%20in%20Ahmedabad%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20isn%E2%80%99t%20business%20as%20usual%20for%20Indian%20cricket%20fandom.%20It%20breeds%20a%20sense%20of%20exclusion%20and%20anxiety%20and%20shall%20steadily%20drive%20people%20away%20from%20stadiums.%20If%20not%20nipped%20in%20the%20bud%2C%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20too%20long%20before%20more%20cities%20catch%20up%20with%20it.%20And%20that%20won%E2%80%99t%20make%20for%20a%20very%20pretty%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697625037000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18151955%2FF8aL8TQaAAAtZFh.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fahmedabad-and-the-art-of-weaponising-an-india-pakistan-spectacle%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Narendra%20Modi%20stadium%20has%20in%20a%20short%20time%20managed%20to%20shift%20the%20fan%20culture%20to%20be%20more%20representative%20of%20the%20politics%20its%20benefactors%20stand%20for.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fahmedabad-and-the-art-of-weaponising-an-india-pakistan-spectacle%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Musk's%20X%20tests%20making%20new%20users%20pay%20to%20post%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697624280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-twitter-x-elon-musk_6310517.jpg%3F20231006005731%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Felon-musks-x-formerly-twitter-tests-making-new-users-pay-to-post-12986899%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20X%20has%20started%20testing%20a%20potential%20sign-up%20fee%20for%20new%20users.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A192%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Felon-musks-x-formerly-twitter-tests-making-new-users-pay-to-post-12986899%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Felon-musks-x-formerly-twitter-tests-making-new-users-pay-to-post-12986899%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Felon-musks-x-formerly-twitter-tests-making-new-users-pay-to-post-12986899%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inclusion%20of%20Meiteis%20in%20ST%20List%20Rejected%20in%201982%2C%202001%2C%20Historical%20Documents%20Kept%20From%20Manipur%20HC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F12163734%2Fmaxresdefault_live.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Appeals%20to%20grant%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20status%20to%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Meitei%20community%20have%20been%20rejected%20twice%20in%20the%20last%2040%20years%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fst-status-for-meiteis-was-considered-and-rejected-in-1982-and-2001-government-records-show%2Farticle67420818.ece%5C%22%3Edocuments%20accessed%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20was%20examined%20and%20rejected%2C%20first%2C%20in%201982%2C%20by%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20Registrar%20General%20of%20India%20(RGI)%3B%20and%20again%2C%20in%202001%2C%20by%20the%20Manipur%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Union%20and%20Manipur%20governments%20did%20not%20make%20this%20information%20public%20during%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20conflict%20in%20the%20state%2C%20nor%20presented%20these%20records%20in%20the%20Manipur%20high%20court%20case%20on%20the%20Meitei%20petition%20for%20inclusion%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fst-status-for-meiteis-was-considered-and-rejected-in-1982-and-2001-government-records-show%2Farticle67420818.ece%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20tribal%20affairs%20ministry%20fished%20out%20the%20old%20documents%20just%20days%20after%20the%20Manipur%20high%20court%20order%20to%20consider%20ST%20status%20for%20Meiteis%20was%20made%20public.%20After%20the%20judgment%2C%20the%20state%20saw%20violence%20between%20the%20Meitie%20and%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20communities%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%20nearly%20180%20people%20and%20engulfed%20Manipur%20in%20a%20five-month%20long%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrevious%20requests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20records%2C%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20under%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%2C%202005%2C%20showed%20that%20the%20RGI%E2%80%99s%20office%20had%20looked%20into%20the%20Meiteis%E2%80%99%20inclusion%20in%20the%20ST%20list%20on%20a%20request%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20in%201982.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20RGI%E2%80%99s%20office%20found%20that%20based%20on%20%E2%80%9Cavailable%20information%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Meitei%20community%20%E2%80%9Cdoes%20not%20appear%20to%20possess%20tribal%20characteristics%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20said%20that%20it%20was%20not%20in%20favour%20of%20inclusion.%20It%20noted%20that%20historically%2C%20the%20term%20had%20been%20used%20to%20describe%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnon-tribal%20population%20in%20the%20Manipur%20valley%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdespite-repeated-requests-pm-modi-avoids-meeting-manipur-bjp-mlas%5C%22%3EDespite%20Repeated%20Requests%2C%20PM%20Modi%20Avoids%20Meeting%20Manipur%20BJP%20MLAs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202001%2C%20the%20erstwhile%20social%20justice%20ministry%20had%20sought%20the%20Manipur%20government%E2%80%99s%20recommendation%20while%20revising%20the%20SC%2FST%20lists%20of%20states%20and%20Union%20territories.%20In%20response%2C%20the%20Tribal%20Development%20Department%20of%20Manipur%2C%20on%20January%203%2C%202001%2C%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fst-status-for-meiteis-was-considered-and-rejected-in-1982-and-2001-government-records-show%2Farticle67420818.ece%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Union%20that%20it%20agreed%20with%20the%201982%20opinion%20of%20the%20RGI%20on%20the%20status%20of%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThen%20chief%20minister%20of%20Manupur%2C%20W.%20Napamacha%20Singh%2C%20had%20said%20that%20the%20Meitei%20community%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdominant%20group%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%9D%20and%20need%20not%20be%20included%20in%20the%20ST%20list.%20It%20noted%20that%20Meitei%20people%20were%20Hindus%20and%20%E2%80%9Cassumed%20the%20status%20of%20Kshatriya%20Caste%20in%20the%20ladder%20of%20Hindu%20Castes%E2%80%9D%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20had%20already%20been%20listed%20as%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20documents%20were%20not%20submitted%20to%20the%20single%20judge%20bench%20of%20Acting%20Chief%20Justice%20M.V.%20Muralidharan%20who%20was%20hearing%20the%20Meiteis%E2%80%99%20petition%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20criteria%20for%20inclusion%20in%20the%20ST%20list%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20criteria%20followed%20by%20the%20RGI%20to%20determine%20whether%20a%20community%20should%20be%20included%20in%20the%20ST%20list%20were%20set%20in%201965%20and%20are%20followed%20even%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20proposal%20to%20change%20this%20criteria%2C%20based%20on%20an%20internal%20committee%E2%80%99s%20report%2C%20was%20floated%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Tribal%20Affairs%20in%202014%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20government%20came%20to%20power.%20In%202022%2C%20officials%20said%20there%20were%20no%20plans%20to%20change%20the%20decades-old%20criteria%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20one%20of%20the%20recommendations%20made%20by%20the%20internal%20committee%20was%20to%20not%20discount%20a%20community%E2%80%99s%20plea%20for%20inclusion%20in%20the%20ST%20list%20solely%20based%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20were%20followers%20of%20Hinduism%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697623208000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F12163734%2Fmaxresdefault_live.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Finclusion-of-meiteis-in-st-list-rejected-in-1982-2001-historical-documents-kept-from-manipur-hc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20documents%20were%20not%20submitted%20to%20the%20single%20judge%20bench%20of%20Acting%20Chief%20Justice%20M.V.%20Muralidharan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Finclusion-of-meiteis-in-st-list-rejected-in-1982-2001-historical-documents-kept-from-manipur-hc%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22British%20man%20and%20his%20wife%20murdered%20on%20honeymoon%20in%20Uganda%22%2C%22content%22%