e%20upcoming%20elections%2C%20the%20power%20tussle%20between%20his%20party%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20the%20issues%20at%20stake%20in%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20is%20known%20to%20alternate%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20governments%20every%20five%20years.%20However%2C%20Dotasra%20is%20confident%20that%20his%20party%2C%20this%20time%20around%2C%20will%20buck%20the%20trend%2C%20by%20re-electing%20the%20Congress%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWill%20the%20people%20of%20Rajasthan%20look%20for%20Modi%20%3Cem%3EJi%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Nadda%3Cem%3E%20Ji%3C%2Fem%3E%20if%20the%20BJP%20comes%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state%3F%20We%20are%20here%2C%20available%20for%20the%20people%20and%20we%20will%20be%20here%20even%20after%20elections%20unlike%20Nadda%20and%20Prime%20Minister%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dotasra%2C%20countering%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20centred%20around%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20its%20national%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWord%20has%20it%20that%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20central%20election%20committee%20has%20already%20cleared%20the%20names%20of%20its%20candidates%20for%20106%20out%20of%20200%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20list%20of%20nominees%20could%20be%20out%20anytime%20soon.%20The%20BJP%2C%20for%20its%20part%2C%20has%20released%20its%20list%20of%20nominees%20for%2041%20seats%20so%20far%2C%20which%20has%20sparked%20discontent%20in%20the%20party.%20Vasundhara%20Raje%E2%80%99s%20camp%20feels%20her%20faction%20in%20the%20party%20has%20been%20sidelined%2C%20with%20the%20party%20ignoring%20the%20names%20proposed%20by%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBelow%20are%20the%20excerpts%20from%20Dotasra%E2%80%99s%20interview%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20is%20a%20criticism%20that%20people%20are%20disappointed%20with%20the%20Congress%20government%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3ERight%20to%20Health%20scheme%20because%20private%20hospitals%20are%20not%20being%20able%20to%20manage%20patients.%20People%20now%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20hours%20for%20their%20turn%20in%20private%20hospitals.%20Do%20you%20feel%20that%20your%20government%20has%20been%20too%20hasty%20in%20implementing%20the%20scheme%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20this%20initiative%2C%20which%20we%20have%20taken%20in%20the%20state%2C%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20undertaken%20by%20any%20other%20state%20in%20the%20country.%20In%20Rajasthan%2C%20people%20are%20getting%20free%20healthcare.%20Also%2C%20if%20you%20see%20in%20Chiranjivi%20Yojna%2C%20people%20are%20getting%20health%20insurance%20as%20well.%20I%20believe%20we%20are%20doing%20better%20compared%20to%20any%20other%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20spoke%20about%20the%20healthcare%20system%2C%20comparing%20it%20to%20other%20states.%20There%20is%20one%20more%20thing%20that%20is%20being%20compared%20to%20other%20states%2C%20i.e.%2C%20NCRB%20data%2C%20which%20says%20that%20Rajasthan%20has%20recorded%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20rape%20cases.%20What%20do%20you%20have%20to%20say%20about%20this%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20agree%20with%20this%20because%20there%20is%20a%20difference%20between%20registering%20an%20FIR%20and%20getting%20convicted.%20In%20our%20state%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20we%20do%20is%20to%20register%20an%20FIR%2C%20because%20we%20believe%20in%20taking%20action%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FYGH0SN_BOHw%3Fsi%3DyKiDKZLJ3W9CPOkb%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeven%20BJP%20MPs%20will%20be%20contesting%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20election.%20Do%20you%20think%20the%20Congress%20will%20face%20a%20tough%20fight%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20we%20