peg%20553w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18132418%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-18-at-1.18.14-PM-138x300.jpeg%20138w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18132418%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-18-at-1.18.14-PM-472x1024.jpeg%20472w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680617%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22625%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20email%20Safina%20Nabi%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ENabi%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20institute%20had%20made%20arrangements%20for%20her%20to%20travel%20for%20the%20award%20ceremony%2C%20and%20she%20was%20supposed%20to%20leave%20on%20October%2017%20for%20Pune.%20However%2C%20on%20the%20afternoon%20of%20October%2016%2C%20she%20received%20a%20call%20from%20an%20unknown%20faculty%20member%20who%20said%20the%20award%20had%20been%20cancelled%20and%20so%20she%20should%20no%20longer%20travel%20to%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEverything%20was%20in%20place%20and%20for%20a%20week%20they%20kept%20reaching%20out%20for%20travel%20arrangements%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20supposed%20to%20travel%20on%20the%2017th%20of%20October%20and%20on%20the%2016th%20of%20October%20around%202%20o%E2%80%99clock%20in%20the%20afternoon%20I%20received%20a%20call%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20phone%20was%20a%20woman%20who%20introduced%20herself%20as%20one%20of%20the%20faculty%20members%20of%20the%20university.%20She%20mentioned%20that%20they%20are%20canceling%20my%20award%20and%20I%20am%20not%20supposed%20to%20travel%20now.%20When%20I%20asked%20for%20the%20reasons%20she%20mentioned%20that%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20political%20pressure%20that%20they%20are%20facing%20for%20awarding%20me.%20She%20also%20said%20it%20would%20be%20highly%20risky%20for%20me%20to%20travel%20or%20be%20present%20at%20the%20venue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThinking%20that%20this%20was%20some%20sort%20of%20a%20prank%20call%2C%20Nabi%20then%20reached%20out%20to%20Rajeesh%20Kumar%20who%20is%20an%20assistant%20professor%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Mass%20Communication%20and%20Journalism%20to%20check%20about%20the%20authenticity%2C%20as%20he%20had%20been%20her%20single%20point%20of%20contact%20till%20then.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20my%20surprise%2C%20he%20was%20clueless%20and%20requested%20to%20be%20given%20some%20time%20to%20cross-check%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20called%20me%20back%20sometime%20and%20confirmed%20that%20they%20were%20actually%20canceling%20my%20award%20and%20he%20was%20sorry.%20I%20requested%20they%20put%20all%20of%20this%20over%20email%20and%20give%20me%20the%20reasons%20as%20to%20why%20are%20they%20doing%20so.%20After%20this%20Dhiraj%20Singh%20called%20me%20who%20mentioned%20the%20same%20thing%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20agree%20to%20put%20anything%20over%20email.%20They%20were%20just%20calling%20me%20and%20giving%20me%20the%20reason%20that%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20political%20pressure%20on%20the%20university%20not%20to%20felicitate%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ENabi%20then%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20jury%2C%20who%20too%20had%20not%20been%20told%20about%20the%20cancellation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20learning%20about%20the%20cancellation%20of%20Nabi%E2%80%99s%20award%2C%20which%20was%20publicly%20announced%20by%20the%20institute%20in%20a%20press%20statement%20last%20Saturday%2C%20the%20jury%20members%20refused%20to%20attend%20the%20event%20where%20they%20were%20to%20participate%20in%20a%20discussion%20on%20%E2%80%9Cmedia%20and%20democracy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJury%20members%20say%20they%20were%20%E2%80%9Cshocked%E2%80%9D%20to%20hear%20about%20the%20award%20being%20cancelled.%20%E2%80%9CThree%20jury%20members%20were%20in%20Pune%20to%20attend%20the%20event%20and%20participate%20in%20a%20discussion%20(Sunanda%2C%20Sandeep%20and%20I).%20On%20learning%20of%20the%20cancellation%2C%20we%20discussed%20amongst%20ourselves%20and%20decided%20that%20the%20best%20statement%20to%20make%20would%20be%20to%20not%20attend%20the%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20Venu%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKashmiri%20journalists%20are%20being%20subjected%20to%20altogether%20different%20level%20of%20censorship%20and%20harassment%20which%20is%20totally%20unconscionable.%20That%20too%20led%20to%20my%20decision%20not%20to%20attend%20the%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20Venu%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reached%20out%20to%20director%2C%20Department%20of%20Media%20%26amp%3B%20Communication%20at%20MIT-WPU%20Dhiraj%20Singh%20to%20ask%20why%20the%20award%20has%20been%20cancelled.%20This%20article%20will%20be%20updated%20when%20a%20response%20is%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697619245000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18132821%2Fheadshot_safina_nabi_1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fpune-institute-cancels-award-for-kashmiri-journalist-jury-refuses-to-attend-event-in-protest%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Safina%20Nabi%E2%80%99s%20report%20had%20been%20unanimously%20chosen%20as%20the%20winner%20of%20a%20media%20award%20instituted%20by%20the%20journalism%20school%20run%20by%20the%20Maharashtra%20Institute%20of%20Technology-World%20Peace%20University.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A86%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fpune-institute-cancels-award-for-kashmiri-journalist-jury-refuses-to-attend-event-in-protest%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'I%20was%20groaning%20in%20pain'%3A%20World's%20new%20hottest%20chilli%20revealed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697617200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F70x70%2Fskynews-pepper-hottest-world_6325340.jpg%3F20231018081248%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fpepper-x-named-