ced%20Raj%E2%80%99s%20behaviour%20and%20advised%20him%20to%20see%20the%20campus%20therapist.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F315631%2Fbengaluru-punita-mittal-mahak-maheshwari-soulup-mental-health-online-support-platform%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseeing%20a%20therapist%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20like%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%20for%20me%20as%20I%20had%20made%20up%20my%20mind%20that%20there%20was%20no%20end%20to%20the%20suffering.%20In%20that%20two-hour%20long%20session%2C%20I%20just%20vented%20out.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20therapist%20was%20a%20great%20listener%20and%20he%20helped%20me%20realise%20that%20I%20have%20to%20talk%20through%20my%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20So%20Raj%20continued%20to%20visit%20the%20therapist%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317358%2Fmodel-dinesh-mohan-silver-fox-narrates-battle-with-eating-disorder-and-depression%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20fight%20depression%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CFighting%20depression%20is%20not%20a%20linear%20journey%3B%20it%20is%20not%20like%20you%20are%20in%20and%20then%20out%20of%20it.%20It%20is%20a%20combination%20of%20relapses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98There%20is%20light%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20tunnel%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCxasLGkv9Ni%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCxasLGkv9Ni%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%