%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F195317%2Flifestyle-compost-bucket-home-kitchen-waste-organic-garden-diy-order-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekitchen%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20makes%20bio%20enzymes%20from%20neem%20leaves%2C%20marigolds%2C%20orange%20peels%2C%20lemons%2C%20and%20bananas.%20%E2%80%9CThree%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20programme%20on%20DD%20Kisan%20that%20highlighted%20the%20importance%20of%20using%20bio%20enzymes.%20I%20realised%20these%20are%20easy%20to%20make%20and%20have%20numerous%20benefits%20like%20boosting%20plant%20growth%20and%20protecting%20plants%20from%20insects%20and%20fungus%20attacks.%20Enzymes%20act%20as%20both%20fertilisers%20and%20insecticides%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20homemaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENita%20shares%20five%20easy%20tips%20on%20how%20to%20make%20bio%20enzymes%20from%20kitchen%20and%20garden%20waste%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFollow%20the%203%3A1%3A10%20formula%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20ingredient%20needed%20to%20make%20bio%20enzymes%20can%20be%20neem%2C%20lemon%20peels%2C%20banana%20peels%2C%20etc.%20Apart%20from%20that%20you%20would%20need%20jaggery%20and%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCut%20the%20main%20ingredients%20into%20small%20parts%2C%20then%20mix%20300%20grams%20of%20this%20with%20100%20grams%20of%20jaggery%20in%201%2C000%20ml%20of%20water.%20Mix%20the%20contents%20well.%20Irrespective%20of%20the%20main%20ingredient%2C%20one%20should%20add%20contents%20in%20their%20respective%20ratio%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENita%20adds%20that%20marigold%20enzyme%20enhances%20flowering%20growth%2C%20while%20orange%20and%20lemon%20peels%20aid%20the%20growth%20of%20plants%20like%20roses%20and%20lilies%20in%20acidic%20soil.%20Neem%20enzyme%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20serves%20as%20an%20insecticide%20or%20fungicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3