issing-people-dementia-autism-upsc%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edifferent%20types%20of%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdis%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%20Starting%20with%20the%20crowd%20favourites%20like%20dal%2C%20%3Cem%3Epalak%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spinach)%20and%20mixed%20vegetable%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20menu%20moves%20on%20to%20fancier%20varieties%20like%20cheese%20chilly%2C%20%3Cem%3Epalak%20paneer%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20pav%20bhaji%2C%20kolhapuri%2C%20corn%20mushroom%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20more.%20Their%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdis%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20priced%20between%20Rs%20209-349%20and%20are%20served%20with%20a%20papad%2C%20work%20as%20a%20whole%20meal%2C%20adds%20Abha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWithin%20the%20first%20month%20of%20business%2C%20they%20earned%20enough%20to%20pay%20their%20staff%20members%20their%20salary%2C%20which%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20rewarding%20moments%20in%20her%20life%2C%20says%20the%20businesswoman.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20able%20to%20pay%20someone%20a%20salary%2C%20which%20was%20the%20same%20amount%20which%20I%20got%20in%20my%20first%20job%2C%20I%20felt%20so%20happy.%20What%20added%20to%20the%20happiness%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20was%20from%20the%20profits%20and%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20take%20any%20loan%20or%20investment%20for%20the%20same%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBuoyed%20by%20the%20sales%2C%20they%20opened%20their%20second%20branch%20in%20Mumbai%20within%20six%20months.%20Today%2C%20they%20have%20eight%20branches%20across%20Mumbai%20and%20Hyderabad%2C%20with%20plans%20of%20opening%20three%20more%20in%20Hyderabad%20this%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20saw%20everyone%20moving%20to%20healthier%20consumption%20and%20one%20of%20the%20food%20items%20prescribed%20by%20doctors%20is%20always%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20be%20it%20the%20dal%20khichdi%20in%20the%20north%20to%20your%20%3Cem%3Epongal%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20south.